              <span id="reviewTextContainer3023903335" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer3367389380224759960">I&apos;ve listened to the book and I still cannot wrap my head around this story. There were true horrors experienced by members of this flight and I&apos;m really just astounded by their perseverance.</span>
  <span id="freeText3367389380224759960" style="display:none">I've listened to the book and I still cannot wrap my head around this story. There were true horrors experienced by members of this flight and I'm really just astounded by their perseverance.</span>
